                        "name": "Delayed Suggestion",
                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "When a veiled master successfully casts <a aonid=\"87\" game-obj=\"Spells\"><i>dominate</i></a> on a creature, a <a aonid=\"315\" game-obj=\"Spells\"><i>suggestion</i></a> spell triggers when the <a aonid=\"87\" game-obj=\"Spells\"><i>dominate</i></a> spell ends. This <a aonid=\"315\" game-obj=\"Spells\"><i>suggestion</i></a> usually causes the target to return to the veiled master, so the creature can cast <a aonid=\"87\" game-obj=\"Spells\"><i>dominate</i></a> again, but a veiled master can set the <a aonid=\"315\" game-obj=\"Spells\"><i>suggestion</i></a> to different orders if it wishes.",
